messages.message: We store all detected tables with LLM generated table summary names in an internal db. So we can fetch all table names in a given document (we already fetch all table content with provenance when we show all tables for each document).
Interesting so the table names are also generated post identification? @Vishnu for table highlighting, do we use that generated table name as the answer?
Yes correct table names are also generated during document indexing (part of table detection and ingestion).
